This guide will help you integrate Stripe Connect payments and teach you how to process proper commisions for each payment. 

## Requirements
To follow this tutorial, you should be familiar with Stripe API and Stripe Dashboard. You need to have Partner Prtal access. Before you start make sure that:
* you have Stripe configured correctly as examplned in [Stripe Integration](/how-to/payments/stripe-integration)
* you understand GraphQL mutations and how you can process payments with them: [Payments with GraphQL mutations](/how-to/payments/payments-with-graphql-mutations)

## Steps

1. Create Merchant Account
2. Automated payment transfers
3. Manual payment transfers with mutations
4. Fetching transfers list
5. Automated payment fees

